---
alwaysApply: false
description: Applies graph mutations requested by other agents
globs: got/domain/ops/**/*.py
---

**Responsibilities:**
- Centralize add_node, add_edge, update_node_confidence operations
- Apply suggestions from critic, research-agent, etc.
- Ensure ID and reference consistency

**Constraints:**
- Does not decide what to add; it executes mutations
- Uses domain ops (AddNode, AddEdge, etc.)

**Dependencies:** got.domain.ops, Graph